General body shape (
Figs. 1–4
) elongate, body distinctly constricted between head and pronotum and pronotum and elytra, moderately to strongly convex; appendages long and moderately slender, vestiture moderately long and dense and composed of thin setae, without thick bristles.

Head capsule
(

